3641	    \operatorname{coverOpen} \mathcal{U}\, i \;=\; D(s_i)
3642	    \quad\text{in } \mathrm{Opens}(\operatorname{Spec} R).
3643	  \]
3644	  This identifies the opens of a standard cover with distinguished opens, which is the form in
3645	  which a standard cover is recognised inside the basis \(\mathcal{B}\) of the affine cover system.
3646	\end{lemma}
